data.description: Beautiful Ranch home in the highly desirable Lindberg Village Subdivision. The spilt floor plan features cathedral ceilings in the living room and kitchen. Highlights include a large kitchen with an island and a large desk area, Whirlpool stainless steel appliances, including a brand-new gas range and an abundance of cabinets and pantry space. Relax with your morning coffee in the sunroom adjacent to the kitchen with 3 walls of windows. The large Primary Suite features a very large walk-in closet, recently remodeled on-suite with a large garden jetted & heated tub for those long hot soaks, double vanities, massive custom tile walk-in shower with 3 shower heads. This property also includes a coveted 3-car garage, providing ample space for your vehicles and storage needs with custom built shelving. Enjoy the well-maintained landscape and fenced backyard. Recently painted throughout and brand-new carpeting in all 3 bedrooms. Don't miss the opportunity to have this beautiful property your home sweet home!
